distressing to her.

00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:59.890 align:middle line:84%
She kept feeling that maybe
she was losing her mind.

00:12:59.890 --> 00:13:03.920 align:middle line:84%
Certainly she couldn't
reconcile all of this activity

00:13:03.920 --> 00:13:07.380 align:middle line:84%
with her scientific
predilections.

00:13:07.380 --> 00:13:12.140 align:middle line:84%
And this became a particularly
acute problem for her

00:13:12.140 --> 00:13:16.650 align:middle line:84%
as the summer and
early fall began.

00:13:16.650 --> 00:13:21.590 align:middle line:84%
One night she called me, and
this was in October, and said,

00:13:21.590 --> 00:13:25.500 align:middle line:84%
you know that inner
voice refuses to go away.

00:13:25.500 --> 00:13:29.710 align:middle line:84%
It keeps saying, this
is a course in miracles.

00:13:29.710 --> 00:13:31.350 align:middle line:90%
Please take notes.

00:13:31.350 --> 00:13:32.080 align:middle line:90%
What shall I do?

00:13:32.080 --> 00:13:33.180 align:middle line:90%
Suppose it's crazy.

00:13:33.180 --> 00:13:34.630 align:middle line:84%
Suppose it doesn't
make any sense.

00:13:34.630 --> 00:13:36.560 align:middle line:90%
Suppose it's flipped.

00:13:36.560 --> 00:13:39.520 align:middle line:84%
And she was obviously
going through a great deal

00:13:39.520 --> 00:13:42.230 align:middle line:84%
of anguish and
agony at that point.

00:13:42.230 --> 00:13:45.070 align:middle line:90%
I said the only obvious thing.

00:13:45.070 --> 00:13:47.560 align:middle line:84%
Why don't you take
down whatever it is?

00:13:47.560 --> 00:13:50.410 align:middle line:84%
You can read it to me tomorrow
morning in the office,

00:13:50.410 --> 00:13:51.840 align:middle line:84%
and if it doesn't
make any sense,

00:13:51.840 --> 00:13:54.530 align:middle line:84%
no one else ever has
to know about it.

00:13:54.530 --> 00:13:57.040 align:middle line:84%
But at least we'll
know what it is.

00:13:57.040 --> 00:13:58.670 align:middle line:90%
So that's what we did.

00:13:58.670 --> 00:14:01.290 align:middle line:90%
The next morning, Helen came in.

00:14:01.290 --> 00:14:04.550 align:middle line:84%
And as she read that
beautiful introduction

00:14:04.550 --> 00:14:09.550 align:middle line:84%
to the text, which says
nothing real can be threatened.

00:14:09.550 --> 00:14:12.510 align:middle line:90%
Nothing unreal exists.

00:14:12.510 --> 00:14:16.730 align:middle line:90%
Herein lies the peace of God.

00:14:16.730 --> 00:14:19.630 align:middle line:84%
It was obvious that we
were tuning into something

00:14:19.630 --> 00:14:23.190 align:middle line:84%
that could hardly be
regarded as crazy, no matter

00:14:23.190 --> 00:14:27.250 align:middle line:90%
how unexpected it was.

00:14:27.250 --> 00:14:30.140 align:middle line:84%
>>A major contribution
of miracles

00:14:30.140 --> 00:14:32.340 align:middle line:84%
is their strength
in releasing you

00:14:32.340 --> 00:14:35.630 align:middle line:84%
from your false sense of
isolation, deprivation,

00:14:35.630 --> 00:14:36.571 align:middle line:90%
and lack.

00:14:36.571 --> 00:14:41.290 align:middle line:90%


00:14:41.290 --> 00:14:45.720 align:middle line:90%
A miracle is never lost.

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:50.770 align:middle line:84%
It may touch many people
you have not even met

00:14:50.770 --> 00:14:54.300 align:middle line:84%
and produce undreamed
of changes in situations

00:14:54.300 --> 00:14:55.970 align:middle line:90%
of which you are not even aware.

00:14:55.970 --> 00:15:00.530 align:middle line:90%


00:15:00.530 --> 00:15:05.710 align:middle line:84%
Miracles are natural
signs of forgiveness.

00:15:05.710 --> 00:15:08.940 align:middle line:84%
Through miracles, you
accept God's forgiveness

00:15:08.940 --> 00:15:13.370 align:middle line:90%
by extending it to others.

00:15:13.370 --> 00:15:17.360 align:middle line:84%
I would feel the writing coming
on almost daily, and sometimes

00:15:17.360 --> 00:15:19.730 align:middle line:90%
several times a day.

00:15:19.730 --> 00:15:23.850 align:middle line:84%
Evenings turned out to be a
favorite time for dictation.

00:15:23.850 --> 00:15:26.970 align:middle line:84%
I objected bitterly to
this, and often went to bed

00:15:26.970 --> 00:15:29.740 align:middle line:84%
defiantly without
writing anything.

00:15:29.740 --> 00:15:31.790 align:middle line:90%
But I could not sleep.

00:15:31.790 --> 00:15:36.800 align:middle line:84%
Eventually, I got up in some
disgust and wrote as directed.

00:15:36.800 --> 00:15:39.930 align:middle line:84%
I never knew when I started
a sentence how it would end,

00:15:39.930 --> 00:15:42.170 align:middle line:84%
and the ideas came
so quickly that I

00:15:42.170 --> 00:15:45.280 align:middle line:84%
had trouble keeping
up with them.

00:15:45.280 --> 00:15:48.480 align:middle line:84%
>>Helen could turn it
on or off at any time.

00:15:48.480 --> 00:15:50.750 align:middle line:10%
She could stop in the
middle of a sentence

00:15:50.750 --> 00:15:54.310 align:middle line:10%
without even going back to
reread what she had written

00:15:54.310 --> 00:15:56.970 align:middle line:10%
and continue when
she had a moment.

00:15:56.970 --> 00:16:01.210 align:middle line:84%
She could have a research
conference in mid-sentence.

00:16:01.210 --> 00:16:03.230 align:middle line:90%
It made no difference at all.

00:16:03.230 --> 00:16:05.540 align:middle line:84%
The flow of the
material continued

00:16:05.540 --> 00:16:08.950 align:middle line:90%
without any altered state.

00:16:08.950 --> 00:16:12.250 align:middle line:84%
Helen at no time was
in a trance or anything

00:16:12.250 --> 00:16:15.360 align:middle line:90%
remotely resembling a trance.

00:16:15.360 --> 00:16:20.076 align:middle line:84%
But as I read the material, I
recognized that Helen in no way

00:16:20.076 --> 00:16:21.450 align:middle line:84%
could have written
this material.

00:16:21.450 --> 00:16:26.390 align:middle line:84%
It was totally alien to her
background, to her interests,

00:16:26.390 --> 00:16:30.010 align:middle line:84%
and her mode of
conceptualizing abstract ideas,

00:16:30.010 --> 00:16:33.591 align:middle line:84%
that there's no way
she could've done this.

00:16:33.591 --> 00:16:37.000 align:middle line:84%
>>Where did the
writing come from?

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:40.240 align:middle line:84%
I did not understand the
calm but impressive authority

00:16:40.240 --> 00:16:42.720 align:middle line:90%
with which the voice dictated.

00:16:42.720 --> 00:16:45.550 align:middle line:84%
