00:16:59.580 --> 00:17:01.910 align:middle line:84%
My own reactions to
these references,

00:17:01.910 --> 00:17:04.310 align:middle line:84%
which literally
stunned me at the time,

00:17:04.310 --> 00:17:07.050 align:middle line:84%
have decreased in
intensity and are now

00:17:07.050 --> 00:17:09.439 align:middle line:84%
at a level of wonder
and acceptance.

00:17:09.439 --> 00:17:14.410 align:middle line:90%


00:17:14.410 --> 00:17:18.300 align:middle line:84%
The name of Jesus Christ
as such is but a symbol,

00:17:18.300 --> 00:17:22.790 align:middle line:84%
but it stands for love
that is not of this world.

00:17:22.790 --> 00:17:28.622 align:middle line:90%


00:17:28.622 --> 00:17:31.870 align:middle line:84%
This course comes from
him because his words

00:17:31.870 --> 00:17:34.705 align:middle line:84%
have reached you in a language
you can love and understand.

00:17:34.705 --> 00:17:41.670 align:middle line:90%


00:17:41.670 --> 00:17:45.850 align:middle line:84%
The name of Jesus is the
name of one who was a man,

00:17:45.850 --> 00:17:49.700 align:middle line:84%
but saw the face of
Christ in all his brothers

00:17:49.700 --> 00:17:50.765 align:middle line:90%
and remembered God.

00:17:50.765 --> 00:17:54.390 align:middle line:90%


00:17:54.390 --> 00:17:57.340 align:middle line:90%
Is He the Christ?

00:17:57.340 --> 00:17:59.910 align:middle line:90%
Oh, yes, along with you.

00:17:59.910 --> 00:18:06.910 align:middle line:90%


00:18:06.910 --> 00:18:10.540 align:middle line:84%
>>The first part of the
