what would happen next,

00:19:15.220 --> 00:19:18.570 align:middle line:84%
the third and final
volume was announced

00:19:18.570 --> 00:19:21.390 align:middle line:90%
as the "Manual for Teachers."

00:19:21.390 --> 00:19:26.790 align:middle line:84%
So the total period of time
was approximately seven years

00:19:26.790 --> 00:19:31.380 align:middle line:84%
from the time we began with the
text, including the workbook,

00:19:31.380 --> 00:19:34.000 align:middle line:84%
and finally the
manual for teachers.

00:19:34.000 --> 00:19:36.580 align:middle line:10%
>>I first met Helen and
