Jesus, beyond the relationship

00:20:39.030 --> 00:20:40.795 align:middle line:84%
with Him, beyond
hearing His voice.

00:20:40.795 --> 00:20:42.170 align:middle line:84%
It was like being
in the presence

00:20:42.170 --> 00:20:45.460 align:middle line:84%
almost of an ageless,
timeless wisdom.

00:20:45.460 --> 00:20:47.889 align:middle line:84%
And then within seconds,
she'd go right back down,

00:20:47.889 --> 00:20:49.430 align:middle line:84%
worrying about where
her husband was,

00:20:49.430 --> 00:20:52.240 align:middle line:84%
how come he was
late for supper, and

00:20:52.240 --> 00:20:55.270 align:middle line:84%
concerned about
all mundane things.

00:20:55.270 --> 00:20:59.620 align:middle line:10%
>>I was teaching at New
York University in 1975

00:20:59.620 --> 00:21:03.290 align:middle line:10%
and feeling full up
with an exciting career

00:21:03.290 --> 00:21:06.750 align:middle line:10%
in what we then called
experimental parapsychology,

00:21:06.750 --> 00:21:09.220 align:middle line:10%
or consciousness
research, meeting

00:21:09.220 --> 00:21:13.270 align:middle line:10%
very interesting people,
traveling, speaking.

00:21:13.270 --> 00:21:15.990 align:middle line:84%
And I was feeling a
sort of emptiness.

00:21:15.990 --> 00:21:17.400 align:middle line:90%
I didn't know why.

00:21:17.400 --> 00:21:20.210 align:middle line:84%
