there please help me?

00:21:31.730 --> 00:21:33.630 align:middle line:90%
And I meant it.

00:21:33.630 --> 00:21:36.700 align:middle line:84%
Within a very short
time, I received the help

00:21:36.700 --> 00:21:40.420 align:middle line:84%
I sought, but not in
the form I anticipated.

00:21:40.420 --> 00:21:43.470 align:middle line:84%
A few days after, I was
asked by a good friend

00:21:43.470 --> 00:21:46.290 align:middle line:84%
to accompany him to
meet two professors

00:21:46.290 --> 00:21:49.310 align:middle line:84%
of medical psychology
at Columbia University

00:21:49.310 --> 00:21:51.930 align:middle line:84%
School of Physicians
and Surgeons.

00:21:51.930 --> 00:21:54.690 align:middle line:84%
I went with him, not
knowing what to expect

00:21:54.690 --> 00:21:56.630 align:middle line:90%
or why the meeting.

00:21:56.630 --> 00:21:59.710 align:middle line:84%
But it seemed as if
I was supposed to go.

00:21:59.710 --> 00:22:02.960 align:middle line:84%
And that kind of mood
continued as Bill took us

00:22:02.960 --> 00:22:06.870 align:middle line:84%
