00:22:19.580 --> 00:22:21.450 align:middle line:90%
And I was intimidated.

00:22:21.450 --> 00:22:24.350 align:middle line:84%
And the conversation was going
in all different directions.

00:22:24.350 --> 00:22:28.580 align:middle line:84%
And a little bit bemused, I
found myself turning to Helen

00:22:28.580 --> 00:22:31.580 align:middle line:84%
