know what I meant.

00:22:34.700 --> 00:22:36.360 align:middle line:90%
But she seemed quite startled.

00:22:36.360 --> 00:22:38.890 align:middle line:90%
And she said, I beg your pardon.

00:22:38.890 --> 00:22:41.090 align:middle line:84%
And Bill tried to
soothe the situation.

00:22:41.090 --> 00:22:43.540 align:middle line:84%
