talking among themselves.

00:22:58.730 --> 00:23:00.320 align:middle line:90%
And I looked down at it.

00:23:00.320 --> 00:23:02.590 align:middle line:90%
I opened up the black binder.

00:23:02.590 --> 00:23:04.600 align:middle line:84%
And I turned to
the introduction,

00:23:04.600 --> 00:23:07.280 align:middle line:84%
