given a miracle,

00:23:15.720 --> 00:23:18.050 align:middle line:90%
and that I'd asked for it.

00:23:18.050 --> 00:23:19.550 align:middle line:84%
>>In New York,
Judith Skutch-Whitson

00:23:19.550 --> 00:23:21.960 align:middle line:84%
spent a great deal of
time with Helen Schucman,

00:23:21.960 --> 00:23:24.680 align:middle line:84%
