00:23:33.030 --> 00:23:36.360 align:middle line:90%


00:23:36.360 --> 00:23:39.650 align:middle line:84%
>>Tolerance for
pain may be high,

00:23:39.650 --> 00:23:42.660 align:middle line:90%
but it is not without limit.

