00:56:26.120 --> 00:56:28.180 align:middle line:84%
He's part of the
same faulty thought

00:56:28.180 --> 00:56:30.580 align:middle line:84%
system that you are part
of, and that he also

00:56:30.580 --> 00:56:33.060 align:middle line:90%
yearns as you do to return home.

00:56:33.060 --> 00:56:35.320 align:middle line:84%
And so rather than seeing
my brother or my sister

00:56:35.320 --> 00:56:37.020 align:middle line:84%
as separate and
different from me,

00:56:37.020 --> 00:56:39.820 align:middle line:84%
I see them as people
walking along the same road

00:56:39.820 --> 00:56:41.310 align:middle line:90%
back to heaven as I am.

00:56:41.310 --> 00:56:43.610 align:middle line:84%
And it's the love of
Jesus which really

00:56:43.610 --> 00:56:45.060 align:middle line:90%
helps us make that shift.

00:56:45.060 --> 00:56:48.830 align:middle line:90%


00:56:48.830 --> 00:56:52.847 align:middle line:84%
>>What could you want
forgiveness cannot give?

00:56:52.847 --> 00:56:57.230 align:middle line:90%


00:56:57.230 --> 00:57:00.070 align:middle line:90%
Do you want peace?

00:57:00.070 --> 00:57:03.070 align:middle line:90%
Forgiveness offers it.

00:57:03.070 --> 00:57:11.320 align:middle line:84%
Do you want happiness, a quiet
mind, a certainty of purpose,

00:57:11.320 --> 00:57:14.360 align:middle line:84%
and a sense of worth and beauty
that transcends the world?

00:57:14.360 --> 00:57:16.955 align:middle line:90%


00:57:16.955 --> 00:57:21.171 align:middle line:84%
Do you want care and safety and
the warmth of sure protection

00:57:21.171 --> 00:57:21.670 align:middle line:90%
always?

00:57:21.670 --> 00:57:24.960 align:middle line:90%


00:57:24.960 --> 00:57:29.490 align:middle line:84%
All of this
forgiveness offers you.

00:57:29.490 --> 00:57:33.230 align:middle line:84%
Forgive the world, and you will
understand that everything that

00:57:33.230 --> 00:57:35.610 align:middle line:90%
God created cannot have an end.

00:57:35.610 --> 00:57:38.470 align:middle line:90%


00:57:38.470 --> 00:57:43.330 align:middle line:84%
And nothing he did
not create is real.

00:57:43.330 --> 00:57:47.980 align:middle line:84%
In this one sentence is
our course explained.

00:57:47.980 --> 00:57:50.910 align:middle line:84%
>>There certainly does appear to
be a spiritual awakening going

00:57:50.910 --> 00:57:52.340 align:middle line:90%
on in our age.

00:57:52.340 --> 00:57:55.190 align:middle line:84%
Certainly, if you contrast the
'90s with the '40s and '50s

00:57:55.190 --> 00:57:57.660 align:middle line:84%
when I grew up, things are
certainly much different.

00:57:57.660 --> 00:57:58.910 align:middle line:90%
God is no longer a dirty word.

00:57:58.910 --> 00:58:00.820 align:middle line:90%
Angels are spoken about freely.

00:58:00.820 --> 00:58:02.760 align:middle line:90%
Miracles are talked about.

00:58:02.760 --> 00:58:04.520 align:middle line:84%
And I certainly feel
that the "Course"

00:58:04.520 --> 00:58:08.907 align:middle line:84%
is like an integral part
of that new movement.

00:58:08.907 --> 00:58:10.990 align:middle line:84%
And on that line, I think
it's extremely important

00:58:10.990 --> 00:58:13.199 align:middle line:84%
to mention something that
the "Course" says of itself

00:58:13.199 --> 00:58:14.990 align:middle line:84%
at the beginning of
the "Teacher's Manual."

00:58:14.990 --> 00:58:17.130 align:middle line:84%
And that is that it's not
the only spiritual path.

00:58:17.130 --> 00:58:18.588 align:middle line:84%
In fact, it says
that it's only one

00:58:18.588 --> 00:58:21.505 align:middle line:84%
path among many thousands
of the universal course.

00:58:21.505 --> 00:58:23.130 align:middle line:84%
I think that that's
extremely important

00:58:23.130 --> 00:58:26.520 align:middle line:84%
to mention so that people don't
believe that the "Course" is

00:58:26.520 --> 00:58:29.330 align:middle line:84%
just another dogmatic
set of teachings,

00:58:29.330 --> 00:58:32.092 align:middle line:84%
and that we're seeing the
birth of a new church.

00:58:32.092 --> 00:58:33.550 align:middle line:84%
And Jesus in the
"Course" says also

00:58:33.550 --> 00:58:34.924 align:middle line:84%
that he's not the
only person who

00:58:34.924 --> 00:58:37.930 align:middle line:84%
has awakened from the dream, and
that he's not the only helper,

00:58:37.930 --> 00:58:41.530 align:middle line:84%
that there are dozens
and dozens and dozens.

00:58:41.530 --> 00:58:43.832 align:middle line:84%
But he is one major symbol
for us in the Western world,

00:58:43.832 --> 00:58:45.290 align:middle line:84%
and "A Course in
Miracles," I think

00:58:45.290 --> 00:58:48.074 align:middle line:84%
is a major expression of
his teachings to all of us.

00:58:48.074 --> 00:58:52.030 align:middle line:90%


00:58:52.030 --> 00:58:57.980 align:middle line:84%
>>Beyond the body, beyond the
sun and stars, past everything

00:58:57.980 --> 00:59:00.920 align:middle line:84%
you see and yet
somehow familiar,

00:59:00.920 --> 00:59:04.870 align:middle line:84%
is an arc of golden
light that stretches

00:59:04.870 --> 00:59:09.410 align:middle line:84%
as you look into a great
and shining circle.

00:59:09.410 --> 00:59:12.440 align:middle line:84%
And all the circle fills
with light before your eyes.

00:59:12.440 --> 00:59:18.010 align:middle line:90%


00:59:18.010 --> 00:59:21.600 align:middle line:84%
The edges of the
circle disappear,

00:59:21.600 --> 00:59:27.300 align:middle line:84%
and what is in it is no
longer contained at all.

00:59:27.300 --> 00:59:30.540 align:middle line:84%
The light expands and
covers everything,

00:59:30.540 --> 00:59:35.070 align:middle line:84%
extending to infinity,
forever shining,

00:59:35.070 --> 00:59:38.980 align:middle line:84%
and with no break
or limit anywhere.

00:59:38.980 --> 00:59:44.350 align:middle line:84%
Within it, everything is
joined in perfect continuity.

00:59:44.350 --> 00:59:48.440 align:middle line:84%
Nor is it possible to imagine
that anything could be outside.

00:59:48.440 --> 00:59:51.762 align:middle line:90%


00:59:51.762 --> 00:59:54.780 align:middle line:84%
For there is nowhere
that this light is not.

00:59:54.780 --> 00:59:57.630 align:middle line:90%


00:59:57.630 --> 01:00:03.040 align:middle line:84%
What is a miracle,
but this remembering?

01:00:03.040 --> 01:00:09.325 align:middle line:84%
And who is there in whom
this memory lies not?

01:00:09.325 --> 01:00:14.060 align:middle line:84%
The light in one
awakens it in all.

01:00:14.060 --> 01:00:17.230 align:middle line:84%
And when you see
it in your brother,

01:00:17.230 --> 01:00:21.280 align:middle line:84%
you are remembering
for everyone.

01:00:21.280 --> 01:01:19.830 align:middle line:90%